Title: Object: La Vallée des Tombeaux
Description: View in Valley of the Kings, with mosques in the middle distance, seen from a dessert where men resting in tents in the left foreground, with two camels beside. Aquatint on chine-collé
Curator's comments: See also 1904,0929.225 from the same series.
Associated places: Topographic representation of: Biban el-Muluk (Valley of the Kings - Thebes)
